test-rating.description: GreatSchools Ratings for Idaho are based on the spring 2013 Idaho Standards Achievement Test (ISAT) reading, language usage, math and science results. GreatSchools compared the test results for each grade and subject across all Idaho schools and divided them into 1 through 10 ratings (10 is the best). Please note, private schools are not required to release test results, so ratings are available only for public schools. GreatSchools Ratings cannot be compared across states, because of differences in the states' standardized testing programs. Keep in mind that when comparing schools using GreatSchools Ratings it's important to factor in other information, including the quality of each school's teachers, the school culture, special programs, etc.
